snippet.title: 28 CLEVER CAMPING IDEAS || DIY TRAVEL HACKS TO HELP YOU ON A TRIP
snippet.description:
Brilliant outdoor ideas for adventure lovers

If you can't imagine yourself staying at home every weekend and would rather be lost somewhere in a wild forest, then these camping life hacks are for you! Our collection of smart travel tips and road ideas will definitely help you solve any problem while you're away from home on another adventure.

You don't need to buy a boat if you need one. Instead, try out our recycling DIY ideas - making a boat yourself by reusing a big old plastic bottle. Take a bottle of a size where you can comfortably sit in and cut a hole in it. Attach pool noodles as a safe edging around the cut and fix some wooden planks. They will help you balance the weight in a boat. Take a paddle and you're ready for a new river or lake adventure! Be sure to always wear a life west for safety during your trip üõ∂

You may not take a bucket on your trips, but always take an adhesive tape, because you can DIY almost anything with it, for example, a bucket. Fins a big tree branch and place a plastic bag on it. Now tape it all around with an adhesive tape creating the shape of the bag. The tape bucket is more durable than a plastic bag, you can use it for carrying water or any other goods.

Forget the world around & indulge in some romance with your beloved. Watch the glimpse of a melodious and magical Song ''Diljaniya'' which is beautifully composed by duo Rohan Rohan and this soulful melody is sung by the legend, Sonu Nigam. snippet.title: Serge Gnabry scores HAT TRICK & Lewandowski shines in Bayern's HUGE win vs. Schalke | ESPN FC
snippet.description:
Bayern Munich waste no time in getting off to a flying start with their 2020-21 Bundesliga campaign, scoring three first-half goals in the process from Serge Gnabry, Leon Goretzka and a penalty from Robert Lewandowski. Lewandowski has now scored 18 goals in 21 Bundesliga games vs. Schalke, netting in each of his last 11 meetings in the process. It was one way traffic for a majority of the match for Hansi Flick's men against David Wagner's, who were without USMNT's Weston McKennie (on loan at Juventus). Bayern opened up the floodgates in the second half as Gnabry completed his hat trick, Thomas Muller got on the end of Lewandowski's Rabona cross, Leroy Sane scored his first goal in a Bayern kit and Jamal Musiala also got in on the action to complete the 8-0 win.

snippet.title: HE JUST LEARNED: President Trump Reacts to News of Ruth Bader Ginsburg's Death
snippet.description:
U.S. Supreme Court Justice Ruth Bader Ginsburg died at 87 of metastatic pancreatic cancer, according to the court. She was the oldest sitting member.

Chief Justice John Roberts mourned Ginsburg‚Äôs passing. ‚ÄúOur Nation has lost a jurist of historic stature. We at the Supreme Court have lost a cherished colleague. Today we mourn, but with confidence that future generations will remember Ruth Bader Ginsburg as we knew her ‚Äî a tireless and resolute champion of justice,‚Äù Roberts said in a statement.

Ginsburg had announced in July that she was undergoing chemotherapy treatment for lesions on her liver, the latest of her several battles with cancer.

Born Joan Ruth Bader on March 15, 1933 in Brooklyn, New York, she was the youngest of two children to Nathan and Celia Bader. It was when Ginsburg was in kindergarten that she decided to go by her middle name Ruth, according to Encyclopedia Britannica.

Ginsburg grew up in a low-income, working-class neighborhood of Brooklyn, where her father worked as a merchant and her mother worked at a clothing factory. Her older sister, Marilyn, died of meningitis when Ginsburg was only a baby.  

Watch what‚Äôs happening right NOW from FOX. We are a non-stop stream of breaking news, live events and stories taking place across the nation. Experience news as it occurs with limited commentary and no opinion.

snippet.title: A message from Tyler.
snippet.description:
The new album - Long Violent History - is available now.
100% of net proceeds from the album will support underserved communities in the Appalachian region through the Hickman Holler Appalachian Relief Fund.

Listen/Download and purchase a merch bundle:  
https://smarturl.it/TCLongViolentHistory

To learn more about The Hickman Holler Appalachian Relief Fund: https://smarturl.it/HHARF

United We Stand. Divided We Fall.

"Long Violent History" Lyrics:

It‚Äôs the worst that it‚Äôs been since the last time it happened 
It‚Äôs happening again right in front of our eyes 
There‚Äôs updated footage, wild speculation,
Tall tales, and hearsay, and absolute lies
Being passed off as factual
When actually the actual
Cause is there awkwardly blocking the way
Keeping us all from enjoying our evening
Shoving its roots through the screens in our face

Now what would you get if you heard my opinion
Conjecturin‚Äô on matters that I ain‚Äôt never dreamed
In all my born days as a white boy from Hickman
Based on the way that the world‚Äôs been to me
It‚Äôs called me belligerent,
It‚Äôs took me for ignorant 
But it ain‚Äôt never once made me scared just to be
Could you imagine just constantly worrying 
Kicking, and fighting, and begging to breathe

How many boys could they haul off this mountain 
Shoot full of holes cuffed and laying in the street
‚ÄòTill we‚Äôd come into town in a stark ravin‚Äô anger
Looking for answers and armed to the teeth,
With thirty-aught-sixes, 
And Papaw‚Äôs old pistol.
How many you reckon?
Would it be four or five?
Or would that be the start of a long Violent History of tucking our tails as we try to abide?

#TylerChilders #LongViolentHistory #HickmanHollerAppalachianReliefFund

snippet.title: Testing Art Trends I've Missed #2
snippet.description:
Hey guys! So I wanted to dedicate a video to testing out the art trends that I've noticed around social media in the past year, but have never actually taken the time to try out. 

Last time I did this, I tried hydro dipping and it was a complete mess.....literally. This time I am doing acrylic pour, sometimes called pouring art or fluid art. This is a super satisfying form of art that has been trending for the last couple of years. This is also much bigger than a trend, many professional artists use paint pouring as their primary form of art. I must say, this was so fun to try. It's such a creative, relaxing and super satisfying abstract art form. At the same time, it would be easy for someone at any skill level to create. I hope you enjoy watching my test out this trend for the first time!

Don't forget to check out my train of a hydro dipping video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eaLrWkWuDjw&t=352s&ab_channel=MoriahElizabeth

Here is the kit I am using (affiliate link):   https://amzn.to/3c8X6Ur



___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

snippet.localized.description:
Hey guys! So I wanted to dedicate a video to testing out the art trends that I've noticed around social media in the past year, but have never actually taken the time to try out. 

Last time I did this, I tried hydro dipping and it was a complete mess.....literally. This time I am doing acrylic pour, sometimes called pouring art or fluid art. This is a super satisfying form of art that has been trending for the last couple of years. This is also much bigger than a trend, many professional artists use paint pouring as their primary form of art. I must say, this was so fun to try. It's such a creative, relaxing and super satisfying abstract art form. At the same time, it would be easy for someone at any skill level to create. snippet.description:
So which gang is the city's biggest and baddest?

Cyberpunk 2077, an open-world, action-adventure story from CD PROJEKT RED, is coming to Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and PC on November 19th, 2020, with the version for Google Stadia set to launch the same year. The game will also be playable on Xbox Series X and PlayStation 5 consoles when available.

Pre-order now: https://www.cyberpunk.net/pre-order

About the game:
Cyberpunk 2077 is an open-world, action-adventure story set in Night City, a megalopolis obsessed with power, glamour and body modification. You play as V, a mercenary outlaw going after a one-of-a-kind implant that is the key to immortality. You can customize your character‚Äôs cyberware, skillset and playstyle, and explore a vast city where the choices you make shape the story and the world around you.

Learn more:

snippet.title: Microsoft Duo Durability Test! - How Thin is too Thin?!

Get your first audiobook and access to a monthly selection of Audible Originals for free when you try Audible for 30 days visit https://www.audible.com/jerryrig or text "jerryrig" to 500 500! As soon as I got this phone out of the box, I know I really, really liked it. Two screens for the price of... two? Perfect. How to add custom color Widgets on iOS 14

iOS 14 added widgets to iPhones and you have plenty to choose from including creating a smart stack of widgets.

But you can also get custom widgets like color widgets that show time, date, and battery life.

In this video, I"ll show you have to add color widgets to your iPhone home screen.  This is from a different app and not including in the list of Widgets that come with your iPhone and iOS14.

You can customize these widgets with your favorite color and font style and move them around anywhere on your iPhone screen.

snippet.title: THE UNDEFEATED CODBUSTER GIANT FISH & CHIP CHALLENGE | C.O.B. Ep.171

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Fulham vs Arsenal (0-3) | Willian, Gabriel impress on debuts
snippet.description:
We got off to a flying start in the Premier League with a classy performance and three points at Craven Cottage.

Alex Lacazette, debutant Gabriel and Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang were on target while the outstanding Willian claimed two assists on his first appearance for us.

Fulham were bright in the opening moments and a misjudgement from Gabriel almost let in Aboubakar Kamara. Bernd Leno did well to claw the ball off his toes.

From then on, the home side could not live with our pace, movement and quality.

The first goal was a scrappy one. Mohamed Elneny found Aubameyang and his cutback was fired goalwards by Granit Xhaka. Tim Ream failed to clear, Willian reacted first to force a save from Marek Rodak and Lacazette tucked away the rebound.

Willian struck a free-kick against the base of a post with Rodak beaten, and Aubameyang almost scored from a trademark burst in behind the defence in the left-hand channel.

Gabriel grew in stature as the game unfolded and he marked his debut with a downward header to convert Willian's corner. That effectively put the match to bed very early in the second half.

After that it was a matter of how many we would score, and Aubameyang got the third and final goal thanks to a delightful crossfield pass from Willian and one of the captain's sumptuous finishes into the far corner.

There will be tougher tests ahead, but this was a hugely-encouraging start to the new campaign.

#arsenal #arsenalhighlights #willian #aubameyang #gabrielMagalhaes

Listen to us on Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/show/5yx8txjfb7dMkosumEv6lQ?si=5Ew1dv6wRlCayZ0TQfo-Ug

We are back!

Is Sylvia's relationship going strong? And Nina is dating someone?!
This week, The Thirsty Sisters are here to discuss and catch up on their love lives! 
Will Sylvia admit she's in love? Tune in to find out!


01:45 - Topic of the day
03:00 - Why Sylvia and Nina barely spoke to each other for the past 3 weeks?
03:45 - Nina opening up about her low-key love life
11:45 - Sylvia sharing more about her love life
13:54 - Is love a DHL scam?
22:10 - The differences between Nina and "Betty"'s lifestyle?
24:13 - How does Sylvia determine the importance of people in her life?
28:54 - What's the happiest thing Sylvia and "Mandy" did together?

snippet.description:
MAX ‚Äì Blueberry Eyes (feat. SUGA of BTS) [Official Music Video]

Stream: https://orcd.co/blueberryeyes 
Spotify: http://open.spotify.com/album/2dEJHnsuxIij7YeBbt0sVm
Apple: https://music.apple.com/us/album/colour-vision/1524457751?ls=1

Bringing this music video to life has been such a special experience. I wanted it to feel as if Disney magically made a baby with Wes Anderson in the world of Colour Vision with every bit of our souls intertwined. Emily is my actual wife and she is really pregnant right now with our first child, so art imitates life in a fun way with this video. We studied and memorized all of the Korean lyrics to Suga‚Äôs incredible and romantic verse and all of the blueberries in the bathtub ended up being reused to create limited edition blueberry dyed blueberry eyes shirts. This video is a piece of our hearts and I hope it sparks the same magic in you viewing it as it did for us creating it. Thank you to Suga for being so brilliant on this song and more importantly for being a wonderful friend. Much love.
-MAX

snippet.title: Dune Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Beyond fear, destiny awaits. Watch the trailer for the highly anticipated #DuneMovie now. 


-----------------
https://www.facebook.com/dune
 https://twitter.com/dunemovie
https://www.instagram.com/dunemovie
-----------------

Oscar  nominee  Denis  Villeneuve  (‚ÄúArrival,‚Äù  ‚ÄúBlade  Runner  2049‚Äù)  directs  Warner  Bros.  Pictures  and  Legendary Pictures‚Äô ‚ÄúDune,‚Äù the big-screen adaptation of Frank Herbert‚Äôs seminal bestseller of the same name. A mythic and emotionally charged hero‚Äôs journey, ‚ÄúDune‚Äù tells the story of Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, who must travel to the most dangerous planet  in  the  universe  to  ensure  the  future  of  his  family  and  his  people.  As  malevolent  forces  explode  into conflict over the planet‚Äôs exclusive supply of the most precious resource in existence‚Äîa commodity capable of unlocking humanity‚Äôs greatest potential‚Äîonly those who can conquer their fear will survive.The film stars Oscar nominee Timoth√©e Chalamet (‚ÄúCall Me by Your Name,‚Äù  ‚ÄúLittle Women‚Äù), Rebecca Ferguson  (‚ÄúStephen  King‚Äôs  Doctor  Sleep,‚Äù   ‚ÄúMission:  Impossible  ‚Äì  Fallout‚Äù),  Oscar  Isaac  (the ‚ÄúStar  Wars‚Äù franchise) Oscar nominee Josh Brolin (‚ÄúMilk,‚Äù ‚ÄúAvengers: Infinity War‚Äù), Stellan Skarsg√•rd (HBO‚Äôs ‚ÄúChernobyl,‚Äù ‚ÄúAvengers: Age of Ultron‚Äù), Dave Bautista (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúAvengers: Endgame‚Äù), Stephen McKinley Henderson (‚ÄúFences,‚Äù ‚ÄúLady Bird‚Äù), Zendaya (‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming,‚Äù HBO‚Äôs ‚ÄúEuphoria‚Äù), Chang Chen (‚ÄúMr.  Long,‚Äù ‚ÄúCrouching  Tiger,  Hidden  Dragon‚Äù),    David  Dastmalchian  (‚ÄúBlade  Runner  2049,‚Äù  ‚ÄúThe  Dark  Knight‚Äù), Sharon  Duncan-Brewster  (‚ÄúRogue  One:  A  Star  Wars  Story,‚Äù  Netflix‚Äôs ‚ÄúSex  Education‚Äù),   with  Oscar  nominee Charlotte Rampling (‚Äú45 Years,‚Äù ‚ÄúAssassin‚Äôs Creed‚Äù), with Jason Momoa (‚ÄúAquaman,‚Äù HBO‚Äôs ‚ÄúGame of Thrones‚Äù), and Oscar winner Javier Bardem (‚ÄúNo Country for Old Men,‚Äù ‚ÄúSkyfall‚Äù).   Villeneuve directed ‚ÄúDune‚Äù from a screenplay he co-wrote with Jon Spaihts and Eric Roth based on the novel of the same name written by Frank Herbert.  Villeneuve also produced the film with Mary Parent, Cale Boyter  and  Joe  Caracciolo,  Jr.   The  executive  producers  are  Tanya  Lapointe,  Joshua  Grode,  Herbert  W.  Gains, Jon Spaihts, Thomas Tull, Brian Herbert, Byron Merritt and Kim Herbert. Behind  the  scenes,  Villeneuve  reteamed  with  two-time  Oscar-nominated  production  designer  Patrice  Vermette  (‚ÄúArrival,‚Äù  ‚ÄúSicario,‚Äù  ‚ÄúThe  Young  Victoria‚Äù),  two-time  Oscar-nominated  editor  Joe  Walker  (‚ÄúBlade  Runner  2049,‚Äù  ‚ÄúArrival,‚Äù  ‚Äú12  Years  a  Slave‚Äù),  two-time  Oscar-winning  visual  effects  supervisor  Paul  Lambert  (‚ÄúFirst Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlade Runner 2049‚Äù), and Oscar-winning special effects supervisor Gerd Nefzer (‚ÄúBlade Runner 2049‚Äù).    He  also  collaborated  for  the  first  time  with  Oscar-nominated  director  of  photography  Greig  Fraser  (‚ÄúLion,‚Äù  ‚ÄúZero  Dark  Thirty,‚Äù  ‚ÄúRogue  One:  A  Star  Wars  Story‚Äù);  three-time  Oscar-nominated  costume  designer  
Jacqueline West (‚ÄúThe Revenant,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Curious Case of Benjamin Button,‚Äù ‚ÄúQuills‚Äù) and co-costume designer Bob Morgan; and stunt coordinator Tom Struthers (‚ÄúThe Dark Knight‚Äù trilogy, ‚ÄúInception‚Äù).  Oscar-winning and multiple  Oscar-nominated  composer  Hans  Zimmer  (‚ÄúBlade  Runner  2049,‚Äù  ‚ÄúInception,‚Äù  ‚ÄúGladiator,‚Äù  ‚ÄúThe  Lion King‚Äù) is creating the score.  Warner  Bros.  Pictures  and  Legendary  Pictures  Present  ‚ÄúDune.‚Äù    The  film  is  slated  to  be  released  in  theaters on December 18, 2020.

As  malevolent  forces  explode  into conflict over the planet‚Äôs exclusive supply of the most precious resource in existence‚Äîa commodity capable of unlocking humanity‚Äôs greatest potential‚Äîonly those who can conquer their fear will survive.The film stars Oscar nominee Timoth√©e Chalamet (‚ÄúCall Me by Your Name,‚Äù  ‚ÄúLittle Women‚Äù), Rebecca Ferguson  (‚ÄúStephen  King‚Äôs  Doctor  Sleep,‚Äù   ‚ÄúMission:  Impossible  ‚Äì  Fallout‚Äù),  Oscar  Isaac  (the ‚ÄúStar  Wars‚Äù franchise) Oscar nominee Josh Brolin (‚ÄúMilk,‚Äù ‚ÄúAvengers: Infinity War‚Äù), Stellan Skarsg√•rd (HBO‚Äôs ‚ÄúChernobyl,‚Äù ‚ÄúAvengers: Age of Ultron‚Äù), Dave Bautista (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúAvengers: Endgame‚Äù), Stephen McKinley Henderson (‚ÄúFences,‚Äù ‚ÄúLady Bird‚Äù), Zendaya (‚ÄúSpider-Man: Homecoming,‚Äù HBO‚Äôs ‚ÄúEuphoria‚Äù), Chang Chen (‚ÄúMr.  Long,‚Äù ‚ÄúCrouching  Tiger,  Hidden  Dragon‚Äù),    David  Dastmalchian  (‚ÄúBlade  Runner  2049,‚Äù  ‚ÄúThe  Dark  Knight‚Äù), Sharon  Duncan-Brewster  (‚ÄúRogue  One:  A  Star  Wars  Story,‚Äù  Netflix‚Äôs ‚ÄúSex  Education‚Äù),   with  Oscar  nominee Charlotte Rampling (‚Äú45 Years,‚Äù ‚ÄúAssassin‚Äôs Creed‚Äù), with Jason Momoa (‚ÄúAquaman,‚Äù HBO‚Äôs ‚ÄúGame of Thrones‚Äù), and Oscar winner Javier Bardem (‚ÄúNo Country for Old Men,‚Äù ‚ÄúSkyfall‚Äù).   Villeneuve directed ‚ÄúDune‚Äù from a screenplay he co-wrote with Jon Spaihts and Eric Roth based on the novel of the same name written by Frank Herbert.  Villeneuve also produced the film with Mary Parent, Cale Boyter  and  Joe  Caracciolo,  Jr.   The  executive  producers  are  Tanya  Lapointe,  Joshua  Grode,  Herbert  W.  Gains, Jon Spaihts, Thomas Tull, Brian Herbert, Byron Merritt and Kim Herbert. He  also  collaborated  for  the  first  time  with  Oscar-nominated  director  of  photography  Greig  Fraser  (‚ÄúLion,‚Äù  ‚ÄúZero  Dark  Thirty,‚Äù  ‚ÄúRogue  One:  A  Star  Wars  Story‚Äù);  three-time  Oscar-nominated  costume  designer  
Jacqueline West (‚ÄúThe Revenant,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Curious Case of Benjamin Button,‚Äù ‚ÄúQuills‚Äù) and co-costume designer Bob Morgan; and stunt coordinator Tom Struthers (‚ÄúThe Dark Knight‚Äù trilogy, ‚ÄúInception‚Äù). snippet.title: Young Couple Climb Onto The Housing Ladder With Incredible Tiny Home
snippet.description:
This weeks episode showcases a dynamic young couple and their amazing first tiny home. This home is modern, stylish and was an affordable way for them to get into their very own house in a city where most young people have been priced out of the housing market. 

Especially in cities like Auckland, where the average house price is close to a million dollars, it can be incredibly hard for young people to get onto the housing ladder. This couple thought outside of the box though and decided to start climbing the first step by building an amazing tiny house on wheels!

Laura and Declan have created a spectacular home for themselves. It‚Äôs modern, high quality construction has given them a wonderful first home and a brilliant asset which enables them to escape the rent trap and start building housing security.

snippet.title: Reporter investigates her own father's death in Australia's rural hospitals | 60 Minutes Australia
snippet.description:
Subscribe here: http://9Soci.al/chmP50wA97J Full Episodes: https://9now.app.link/uNP4qBkmN6 | The Greatest Loss (2020)

In a very special edition of 60 MINUTES, Liz Hayes reports on what is the most important, and personal, story of her career. However, it‚Äôs also a story that in modern Australia she shouldn‚Äôt need to tell. It‚Äôs about decent people in the country who are dying because of a rural health system that's broken and failing them. They are people like Liz‚Äôs precious dad. For many years Bryan Ryan was a farmer who lived near Taree, north of Newcastle in NSW. He was 88 years old when he died a year ago, but it‚Äôs highly likely he‚Äôd still be alive today if not for a catastrophic medical error that occurred while he was being treated in the rural health system. Es war zugleich der h√∂chste Sieg in einem Bundesliga-Auftaktspiel, das seit 2002 jeweils der deutsche Meister bestreitet.
